            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿یَشۡهَدُهُ ٱلۡمُقَرَّبُونَ ۝٢١﴾ مِنْ الْمَلَائِكَة</h2>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "83:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿إِنَّ ٱلۡأَبۡرَارَ لَفِی نَعِیمٍ ۝٢٢﴾ جَنَّة</h2>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
                "83:23": {
                    "id": 23
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿عَلَى ٱلۡأَرَاۤىِٕكِ﴾ السُّرَر فِي الْحِجَال ﴿یَنظُرُونَ ۝٢٣﴾ مَا أُعْطُوا مِنْ النَّعِيم</p>"
        },
        "24": {
            "verses": {
                "83:24": {
                    "id": 24
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿تَعۡرِفُ فِی وُجُوهِهِمۡ نَضۡرَةَ ٱلنَّعِیمِ ۝٢٤﴾ بَهْجَة التَّنَعُّم وحسنه</p>"
        },
        "25": {
            "verses": {
                "83:25": {
                    "id": 25
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿یُسۡقَوۡنَ مِن رَّحِیقࣲ﴾ خَمْر خَالِصَة مِنْ الدَّنَس ﴿مَّخۡتُومٍ ۝٢٥﴾ عَلَى إِنَائِهَا لَا يَفُكّ خَتْمه غَيْرهمْ</p>"
        },
        "26": {
            "verses": {
                "83:26": {
                    "id": 26
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿خِتَـٰمُهُۥ مِسۡكࣱۚ﴾ أَيْ آخِر شُرْبه تَفُوح مِنْهُ رَائِحَة الْمِسْك ﴿وَفِی ذَ ٰ⁠لِكَ فَلۡیَتَنَافَسِ ٱلۡمُتَنَـٰفِسُونَ ۝٢٦﴾ فَلْيَرْغَبُوا بِالْمُبَادَرَةِ إِلَى طَاعَة اللَّه</p>"
        },
        "27": {
            "verses": {
                "83:27": {
                    "id": 27
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَمِزَاجُهُۥ﴾ أَيْ مَا يُمْزَج بِهِ ﴿مِن تَسۡنِیمٍ ۝٢٧﴾ فسر بقوله</p>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "83:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿عَیۡنࣰا﴾ فَنَصَبَهُ بِأَمْدَحَ مُقَدَّرًا ﴿یَشۡرَبُ بِهَا ٱلۡمُقَرَّبُونَ ۝٢٨﴾ مِنْهَا أَوْ ضَمَّنَ يَشْرَب مَعْنَى يَلْتَذّ</p>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "83:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿إِنَّ ٱلَّذِینَ أَجۡرَمُوا۟﴾ كَأَبِي جَهْل وَنَحْوه ﴿كَانُوا۟ مِنَ ٱلَّذِینَ ءَامَنُوا۟﴾ كَعَمَّارٍ وَبِلَال وَنَحْوهمَا ﴿یَضۡحَكُونَ ۝٢٩﴾ استهزاء بهم</p>"
        },
        "30": {
            "verses": {
                "83:30": {
                    "id": 30
